IMMEDIATE
No.55/4/CF-68
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
(Department of Cabinet Affairs)
New Delhi, the 27th April,1968.
7th Vaisakha,1890.
The undersigned is directed to state that, with
effect from the afternoon of Saturday, April 27, 1968,
Dr M. Channa Reddy relinquished the office of Minister of
Steel, Mines & Metals,
For the present, Shri Prakashchand B.Sethi, Minister
of State in the Ministry of Steel, Mines & Metals will look
after the work of the Departments of Iron & Steel and Minee
and Metals.
Rmahia
(R N. Kalia)
for Cabinet Secretary.
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy ferwarded to the Secretary to the Primo Minister/
the Joint Secretary to the Prime Minister/the Private Seeretary
to the Prine Minister for information,
Copy forwarded to the Secratary to the President/
the Secretary to the Vice-President, for information.
hauah's
(R, N. Kalia)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
Copy forwarded to all Secretaries/Special Secretaries/
Additional Secretaries to the Government of India/Chairman,
Railway Board/Secretary, Election Commission, for information.
Copy forwarded to all Ministries/Departments of the
Government of India/Lok Sabha Secretariat/Rajya Sabha Secretariat,
for information.
Rumaha
(R.N. Kalia)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
*Monga
250 copies.
